title.rendered: STEDI SQUARE TYPE RJ45 UHF SWITCH INSERT

content.rendered:
Toyota Square UHF RJ45 Switch OEM Style

DETAILS

This RJ45 pass-through connector allows for a UHF fitted with an RJ45 connector to be plugged in.

COMPATIBLE TOYOTA MAKES

  • Toyota Prado 150 Series | 2018 – Onward
  • Fits STEDI 70 series/Ford Ranger custom STEDI switch fascia

SPECIFICATIONS

BACK LIGHT COLOUR Ice Blue Lower and Green Upper
SURFACE SIZE DIMENSIONS 22x22mm
RATED 3A @ 12v

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • 1 x  22 x 22 Square Type UHF RJ45
